content:
Monitor, Update, and Delete Service Intelligence Apps

Use the app management tab to monitor the status of install requests, view logs to troubleshoot install issues, track app usage statistics, and update and delete apps.

From the Setup menu, installed versions of Service Intelligence display as separate tabs. To view details about each app installation, select an app tab. The app details include the installation status, a list of installation events, and the tasks for each event. You can schedule app refreshes or refresh manually and see details of all the installed app resources like dashboards and data transforms.

Manage Your Intelligent Apps
title: Service Cloud App Management
